videos.description: Jarrett Culver takes it to the rim for a one-handed jam to score the game's first basket.
videos.headline: Culver slams for Texas Tech's first bucket

videos.description: Jared Butler picks Matt Mooney's pocket and takes it all the way to extend the Bears' second-half lead.
videos.headline: Butler steals and scores for Baylor

videos.description: Davide Moretti gets the steal and lobs it up for Tariq Owens, who hammers down a two-handed alley-oop in transition.
videos.headline: Moretti lobs, Owens slams
